## ğŸ“Œ Overview

This project performs **end-to-end sentiment analysis** on the **IMDB 50K Movie Reviews Dataset** using **Natural Language Processing (NLP)** and **Machine Learning**.

The goal is to classify movie reviews into **Positive** or **Negative** sentiment with high accuracy using **TF-IDF vectorization and multiple ML models**.

---

## ğŸš€ Key Features

* Complete Data Cleaning & Text Preprocessing
* Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
* TF-IDF Feature Engineering
* Multiple ML Models Training
* Model Comparison & Evaluation
* Confusion Matrix & Performance Visualization
* Topic Modeling using LDA

---

## ğŸ“Š Models Used

* Logistic Regression â­ (Best Performance)
* Naive Bayes
* Linear Support Vector Machine (SVM)
* Random Forest
* Gradient Boosting
* Decision Tree

